These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
City: rome, san-francisco, london, paris, venice, hannover, boston
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, almond-milk, 7up, water, mirinda, milk
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking water is the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| City           | venice | paris | san-francisco | london | rome | hannover | boston |
| Beverage   | coffee    | water   | 7up      | mirinda | almond-milk    | sprite    | milk         |

