.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, july, august, november, december, september, february
City: nizza, liverpool, london, rome, new-york, miami, prague
 1. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Birthday          | october | july | december | november | september | february | august |
| City   | liverpool      | london   | rome   | new-york      | nizza       | prague       | miami     |

