.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, zombie, spy, documentary, action, thriller, family
There are 7 different favourite colors: yellow, purple, red, ebony, black, emerald, pink
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who likes ebony##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
11. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
12. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action     | spy  | thriller       | superhero       | family  | documentary   |
| Color    | emerald  | yellow | pink | ebony | purple | red | black |

