.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, aristoff, tiparillo, dannemann, prince, pall-mall, montecristo
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, nurse, social-worker, architect, engineer, pilot, fisherman
 1. the prince-smoker is the nurse##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 3. the pilot is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the dancer is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the social-worker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the pilot##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is the engineer##1
10. the engineer is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the fisherman is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall    | montecristo     | dannemann     | tiparillo      | aristoff | prince      | blend     |
| Job   | architect | social-worker | pilot | engineer | fisherman | nurse | dancer |

