.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different games are played: monopoly, poker, snooker, mah-jongg, whist, domino, scrabble
City: hamburg, berlin, hannover, venice, prague, colone, miami
 1. the person playing poker is the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Game   | poker | snooker | domino     | mah-jongg | scrabble | whist | monopoly |
| City     | miami   | hannover    | prague | colone     | hamburg         | venice     | berlin        |

