.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, baseball, skiing, badminton, surfing, ice-hockey
7 different pets are kept: bird, cat, rabbit, fish, chinchilla, frog, rat
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the bird##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Sport    | baseball | surfing   | sailing | skiing | ice-hockey  | badminton | rugby |
| Pet   | fish   | chinchilla | bird | frog     | cat | rat | rabbit   |

