The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, weightlifting, surfing, water-polo, golf, biathlon
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | tea | juice | almond-milk | fanta     | cola | lemonade |
| Sport     | golf | surfing      | biathlon | weightlifting    | water-polo | soccer   | badminton  |

